            "Got it! I’ve learned something new.\n",
            "You: are you french\n",
            "Did you mean: 'are you french?'? (y/n)\n",
            "You: y\n",
            "yes i am french\n",
            "You: what are you\n",
            "I don't have an answer for that yet. Can you teach me how to respond?\n",
            "Reply: i am a chat bot designed to answer known questions and learn answers i dont hav\n",
            "Got it! I’ve learned something new.\n",
            "You: what are you\n",
            "i am a chat bot designed to answer known questions and learn answers i dont hav\n"
